name: Playing with Dolls
description: When I was a boy, I was fascinated with the human body. I enjoyed Barbie dolls because of their realistic representation, and removable clothes. This was not something a boy would brag about.  After all these years, nothing has changed… I’m still “playing with Ken and Barbie” and navigating the taboos of nudity.  Here I transform Sawyer Croft into a Barbie, and paint her alongside 10 Barbie dolls.  painted by Roustan - bodypainter.com
